# count-star-to-metadata

## Description

Migrated to a declarative `.rra` rule with a precondition (RFC 0090 Phase 2).

## Rewrite

lhs: (aggregate ?groups ?aggs (scan ?table))
rhs: (metadata-lookup ?table row-count)
when: is_ungrouped_count_star("?groups", "?aggs")
